    </StandardHierarchyLevel>
    <StatementCodes>
      <StatementCode>CCSS.Math.Content.6.NS.C.6</StatementCode>
    </StatementCodes>
    <Statements>
      <Statement>Understand a rational number as a point on the number line. Extend number line diagrams and coordinate axes familiar from previous grades to represent points on the line and in the plane with negative number coordinates.</Statement>
